trans-unit.target: TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_000<tab>Squawk! Trespassing on Ehcatl territory, featherless one is! What business have you with us!?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_001<tab>Squawk! Trespassing on Ehcatl territory, featherless one is! What business have you with us!?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_Q1_000_000<tab>What will you ask?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A1_000_001<tab>Tell me about yourself.
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A1_000_002<tab>What kind of place is this?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A1_000_003<tab>Nothing.
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_010<tab>Guard territory of Ehcatl, Razel does! Step out of line and gut you with talons, Razel will! Squawk!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_011<tab>Gathering of artisans and engineers, this is. Call ourselves “Ehcatl Nine”!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_012<tab>Drawn by dream of Chief Totoloc, we were... Hmmm. To fly again. Yes. To soar!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_013<tab>Snigger at our dreams, do you? Hmmm? Have last cackle, we will! Caw!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_020<tab>Shipyard of Ehcatl Nine, this is!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_021<tab>Obvious, now, what we do here, yes? Building special airship, we are!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_022<tab>Latest technology! Revolutionary ideas! Bind them together to create unique hybrid vessel, we will!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_023<tab>Privileged to be here, featherless one is! Be sneaky and stealthy, we must! Keep camp secret even from our own kin, we do!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_024<tab>Like that we borrow no-feathers technology, they would not!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_025<tab>Caw! Like that we borrow no-feathers technology, no-feathers would not either!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_026<tab>Hide from both, we do! Secret and safe! Blather about what you see here, featherless one must not!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_027<tab>Betray our trust, and mount featherless one's head on airship prow, Razel will! Squawk!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_100<tab>Squawk! <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Have questions for Razel, do you? Hmmm?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_Q2_000_000<tab>What will you ask?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A2_000_001<tab>How fares the Ehcatl Nine?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A2_000_002<tab>What do you do here again?
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_A2_000_003<tab>Nothing.
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_110<tab>Squawk! Well! Very well, we fare!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_111<tab>Great success, first flight of <var 1A 02 /var>Dezul Qualan<var 1A 01 /var> was! Very high, it flew! Soared like bird! But satisfied, we are not...
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_112<tab>Not until we land upon shores of Ayatlan! Dream yet of that day, we do!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_113<tab>And so work, we shall. Today. Tomorrow. Work until we can climb high above clouds, we will! Squawk!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_200<tab>Squawk! Well! Very well, we fare!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_201<tab>Great success, first flight of <var 1A 02 /var>Dezul Qualan<var 1A 01 /var> was! Very high, it flew! Soared like bird! But satisfied, we are not...
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_202<tab>Not until we land upon shores of Ayatlan! Dream yet of that day, we do!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_203<tab>Hmmm? Making solemn face, featherless one is. Strikes awe into heart, name of Ayatlan does? Yes? Then take you there, perhaps we will!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_204<tab>But now work, we must. Today. Tomorrow. Work until we can climb high above clouds, we will! Squawk!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_120<tab>Fall from airship and bump head, did you? Ehcatl, this is! Shipyard of Ehcatl Nine!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_121<tab>Still seek to improve airship, we do!
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_122<tab>Ixal technology, no-feathers technology─it matters not. Only dream of flying.
TEXT_REGFSTEHCATL_00203_RAZELHUIZAN_000_123<tab>Kept Ehcatl secret, you have? Yes? Feel sad about gutting <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, Razel would.
